text: Input/Output Data The Input/Output data is the type of data an agent expects and delivers. The Syslog Collection agent produces SyslogMessageUDR s. MIM This agent does not publish or access any additional MIM parameters. For information about the MIM and a list of the general MIM parameters, see Meta Information Model in MIM .
title: Syslog Collection Agent Input/Output Data and MIM - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
